\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes the requirements for authorized,
 documented,
 supervised,
 and verified maintenance and repair work performed on County IT systems.
 It ensures that all maintenance events are formally authorized before work begins,
 that maintenance records contain the content required for audit reconstruction,
 that data-bearing components are sanitized before leaving County facilities,
 and that systems are verified as correctly and securely operational upon completion of maintenance activity.
\end_layout

